{"captured_at": "2026-07-18T09:36:30.268479Z", "created_at": "Sat Jun 25 14:11:08 +0000 2022", "created_at_iso": "2022-06-25T14:11:08Z", "created_at_ts": 1656166268, "display_name": "Andy Kim", "handle": "andykimnj", "id": "1540699113724907523", "language": "en", "media_json": "[{\"type\": \"photo\", \"url\": \"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/FWGprNGWAAAhJwh.jpg\", \"alt_text\": null}]", "metrics_json": "{\"retweet_count\": 9162, \"reply_count\": 1542, \"like_count\": 34691, \"quote_count\": 1266, \"bookmark_count\": 0, \"view_count\": null}", "source_endpoint": "SyndicationProfile", "tags_json": "[]", "text": "I was on House floor as decision striking Roe was announced. I realized it happened because I saw Marjorie Taylor Greene and others jump up and high five each other. I overheard what they said. One said he always dreamt of this day. Other said something that hit me hard…THREAD https://t.co/GEnGFgP7ku", "tweet_type": "tweet", "urls_json": "[]", "username": "AndyKimNJ"}
{"captured_at": "2026-07-18T09:36:30.268479Z", "created_at": "Sat Jun 25 14:11:10 +0000 2022", "created_at_iso": "2022-06-25T14:11:10Z", "created_at_ts": 1656166270, "display_name": "Andy Kim", "handle": "andykimnj", "id": "1540699122922946560", "language": "en", "media_json": "[{\"type\": \"photo\", \"url\": \"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/FWGprs2WQAAK7f-.jpg\", \"alt_text\": null}]", "metrics_json": "{\"retweet_count\": 2998, \"reply_count\": 366, \"like_count\": 19234, \"quote_count\": 148, \"bookmark_count\": 0, \"view_count\": null}", "source_endpoint": "SyndicationProfile", "tags_json": "[]", "text": "One Republican congressperson said something like “let’s keep this going now.” The words reinforced that this has always been their plan. It’s only the beginning. Republican leadership is hell bent on transforming America by rolling back our rights. Rolling back out progress 2/11 https://t.co/kMzKoNPoAs", "tweet_type": "reply", "urls_json": "[]", "username": "AndyKimNJ"}
{"captured_at": "2026-07-18T09:36:30.268479Z", "created_at": "Sat Jun 25 14:11:13 +0000 2022", "created_at_iso": "2022-06-25T14:11:13Z", "created_at_ts": 1656166273, "display_name": "Andy Kim", "handle": "andykimnj", "id": "1540699136927797250", "language": "en", "media_json": "[{\"type\": \"photo\", \"url\": \"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/FWGpsuvXgAAtKCL.jpg\", \"alt_text\": null}]", "metrics_json": "{\"retweet_count\": 2658, \"reply_count\": 383, \"like_count\": 16068, \"quote_count\": 166, \"bookmark_count\": 0, \"view_count\": null}", "source_endpoint": "SyndicationProfile", "tags_json": "[]", "text": "Next up it’s marriage equality, birth control, gay rights. It’s not speculation as Clarence Thomas made that clear in his published opinion yesterday. Right out in the open for all to see. 3/11 https://t.co/mqUnmXhTNd", "tweet_type": "reply", "urls_json": "[]", "username": "AndyKimNJ"}
{"captured_at": "2026-07-18T09:36:30.268479Z", "created_at": "Sat Jun 25 14:11:15 +0000 2022", "created_at_iso": "2022-06-25T14:11:15Z", "created_at_ts": 1656166275, "display_name": "Andy Kim", "handle": "andykimnj", "id": "1540699145748598785", "language": "en", "media_json": "[{\"type\": \"photo\", \"url\": \"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/FWGptFaUUAAbLjk.jpg\", \"alt_text\": null}]", "metrics_json": "{\"retweet_count\": 2282, \"reply_count\": 265, \"like_count\": 17546, \"quote_count\": 85, \"bookmark_count\": 0, \"view_count\": null}", "source_endpoint": "SyndicationProfile", "tags_json": "[]", "text": "It was disturbing to see lawmakers celebrating the removal of rights from Americans. To see them fist-pumping and hollering in the House chamber. This is a sacred space. The same room where the 19th Amendment passed giving rights to women to vote. 4/11 https://t.co/QCvQtrvyrd", "tweet_type": "reply", "urls_json": "[]", "username": "AndyKimNJ"}
{"captured_at": "2026-07-18T09:36:30.268479Z", "created_at": "Sat Jun 25 14:11:18 +0000 2022", "created_at_iso": "2022-06-25T14:11:18Z", "created_at_ts": 1656166278, "display_name": "Andy Kim", "handle": "andykimnj", "id": "1540699156653539332", "language": "en", "media_json": "[{\"type\": \"photo\", \"url\": \"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/FWGptltUAAE2u9e.jpg\", \"alt_text\": null}]", "metrics_json": "{\"retweet_count\": 1399, \"reply_count\": 105, \"like_count\": 13413, \"quote_count\": 26, \"bookmark_count\": 0, \"view_count\": null}", "source_endpoint": "SyndicationProfile", "tags_json": "[]", "text": "This House chamber is a room meant to protect Americans. To give us rights instead of take them away. To make laws to help solve problems instead of throwing our country into disarray. I walked out of the chamber after votes and headed across the street. I need to step away. 5/11 https://t.co/lpExcegaK6", "tweet_type": "reply", "urls_json": "[]", "username": "AndyKimNJ"}
{"captured_at": "2026-07-18T09:36:30.268479Z", "created_at": "Sat Jun 25 14:11:19 +0000 2022", "created_at_iso": "2022-06-25T14:11:19Z", "created_at_ts": 1656166279, "display_name": "Andy Kim", "handle": "andykimnj", "id": "1540699162957647874", "language": "en", "media_json": "[{\"type\": \"photo\", \"url\": \"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/FWGpuO3WAAYbxim.jpg\", \"alt_text\": null}]", "metrics_json": "{\"retweet_count\": 1696, \"reply_count\": 115, \"like_count\": 13431, \"quote_count\": 62, \"bookmark_count\": 0, \"view_count\": null}", "source_endpoint": "SyndicationProfile", "tags_json": "[]", "text": "I walked across the street to the Supreme Court. Being there at the epicenter felt profound. That this building and 9 people inside could change our way of life. To see words “Equal Justice Under Law” etched into stone but knowing reality of the removal of rights from women. 6/11 https://t.co/IGXIU8YCKu", "tweet_type": "reply", "urls_json": "[]", "username": "AndyKimNJ"}
{"captured_at": "2026-07-18T09:36:30.268479Z", "created_at": "Sat Jun 25 14:11:21 +0000 2022", "created_at_iso": "2022-06-25T14:11:21Z", "created_at_ts": 1656166281, "display_name": "Andy Kim", "handle": "andykimnj", "id": "1540699169870036994", "language": "en", "media_json": "[{\"type\": \"photo\", \"url\": \"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/FWGpuqsWQAE0_xC.jpg\", \"alt_text\": null}]", "metrics_json": "{\"retweet_count\": 1016, \"reply_count\": 37, \"like_count\": 11411, \"quote_count\": 12, \"bookmark_count\": 0, \"view_count\": null}", "source_endpoint": "SyndicationProfile", "tags_json": "[]", "text": "But what was most profound was the feeling of solidarity. The crowd growing up against the perimeter fence. More people showing up by the minute. We chanted loudly as if we could with our voices cancel out the damages emanating from this square block of America. 7/11 https://t.co/7lsyJQKXKP", "tweet_type": "reply", "urls_json": "[]", "username": "AndyKimNJ"}
{"captured_at": "2026-07-18T09:36:30.268479Z", "created_at": "Sat Jun 25 14:11:22 +0000 2022", "created_at_iso": "2022-06-25T14:11:22Z", "created_at_ts": 1656166282, "display_name": "Andy Kim", "handle": "andykimnj", "id": "1540699171774144512", "language": "en", "media_json": "[]", "metrics_json": "{\"retweet_count\": 948, \"reply_count\": 33, \"like_count\": 11000, \"quote_count\": 9, \"bookmark_count\": 0, \"view_count\": null}", "source_endpoint": "SyndicationProfile", "tags_json": "[]", "text": "People there knew that the day was a gut punch. But they didn’t want the Court to have the last word. Thousands of people showed up to say that this dangerous court decision does not reflect America and what we stand for. I felt a profound solidarity. 8/11", "tweet_type": "reply", "urls_json": "[]", "username": "AndyKimNJ"}
{"captured_at": "2026-07-18T09:36:30.268479Z", "created_at": "Sat Jun 25 14:11:26 +0000 2022", "created_at_iso": "2022-06-25T14:11:26Z", "created_at_ts": 1656166286, "display_name": "Andy Kim", "handle": "andykimnj", "id": "1540699192569610240", "language": "en", "media_json": "[{\"type\": \"photo\", \"url\": \"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/FWGpvFEXoAE2vqU.jpg\", \"alt_text\": null}, {\"type\": \"photo\", \"url\": \"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/FWGpvDtWQAATQQ8.jpg\", \"alt_text\": null}]", "metrics_json": "{\"retweet_count\": 785, \"reply_count\": 16, \"like_count\": 10252, \"quote_count\": 6, \"bookmark_count\": 0, \"view_count\": null}", "source_endpoint": "SyndicationProfile", "tags_json": "[]", "text": "I got in my car and drove back home to NJ. I got word that the community was pulling together a rapid response rally. When I arrived I saw hundreds of people with many more pulling up in their cars. The parking lot was overflowing. Cars honking their horns as they passed. 9/11 https://t.co/0JOS3EriEn", "tweet_type": "reply", "urls_json": "[]", "username": "AndyKimNJ"}
{"captured_at": "2026-07-18T09:36:30.268479Z", "created_at": "Sat Jun 25 14:11:29 +0000 2022", "created_at_iso": "2022-06-25T14:11:29Z", "created_at_ts": 1656166289, "display_name": "Andy Kim", "handle": "andykimnj", "id": "1540699203382419456", "language": "en", "media_json": "[{\"type\": \"photo\", \"url\": \"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/FWGpwWdXkAAjcRD.jpg\", \"alt_text\": null}]", "metrics_json": "{\"retweet_count\": 785, \"reply_count\": 28, \"like_count\": 10274, \"quote_count\": 4, \"bookmark_count\": 0, \"view_count\": null}", "source_endpoint": "SyndicationProfile", "tags_json": "[]", "text": "I felt proud. Really proud that my community came together. We showed solidarity. I spoke and said that their energy is my energy and my energy is theirs. We help each other through these tough moments. And our community stood in solidarity with towns all across America 10/11 https://t.co/Ys8OmDIbfR", "tweet_type": "reply", "urls_json": "[]", "username": "AndyKimNJ"}
{"captured_at": "2026-07-18T09:36:30.268479Z", "created_at": "Sat Jun 25 14:11:32 +0000 2022", "created_at_iso": "2022-06-25T14:11:32Z", "created_at_ts": 1656166292, "display_name": "Andy Kim", "handle": "andykimnj", "id": "1540699215998791681", "language": "en", "media_json": "[{\"type\": \"photo\", \"url\": \"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/FWGpxEhVUAQG9_I.jpg\", \"alt_text\": null}]", "metrics_json": "{\"retweet_count\": 4295, \"reply_count\": 323, \"like_count\": 27497, \"quote_count\": 178, \"bookmark_count\": 0, \"view_count\": null}", "source_endpoint": "SyndicationProfile", "tags_json": "[]", "text": "Yesterday we stood with each other in response to the backsliding of rights. But what about today? What about tomorrow?  What about next week or next month? What about November? We need to sustain this solidarity and convert this energy into action. Let’s make that promise. END https://t.co/w4hkqHpfpA", "tweet_type": "reply", "urls_json": "[]", "username": "AndyKimNJ"}
